  "title": "Alternative Zombified Piglins",
  "description": "Makes Zombified Piglins and Zoglins green to match other zombie mobs.",
  "body": "---\n<p align=\"center\"?>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/alternative-zombified-piglins\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bf84aa11b4afd69cdbd20a199bc6d93c50fac58b.png\" \n        alt=\"Modrinth\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        url=\"modrinth.com\"\n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/alternative-zombified-piglins\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3531508338997863e0b15c2252d16bf51ceb5669.png\" \n        alt=\"Curseforge\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/alternative-zombified-piglins\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eac8caa46edda35d821be9a2e1a8e16a00a9cadc.png\" \n        alt=\"Planet Minecraft\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n</p>  \n\n---\nThis resource pack makes Zombified Piglins green to match other zombie mobs. \n\n![Zombified Piglin](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/090a81aadade70eb5072b9533d8aa9ead6dadb7b.png)\n\n---\n<b>(1.16-1.21.3 ONLY) [Optifine](https://optifine.net/downloads) or [Entity Model Features](https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features) and [Entity Texture Features](https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures) recommended</b>, as the default Zombified Piglin model is missing an ear.\n\n![Without/With Optifine or Entity Model Features](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fd6a3b573e2f4e012e0cf7bef28c1f46b3c26d91.png)\n\n---\n",
